# Phase C: Technical EFT Implementation Plan

This document breaks down the specific technical steps to build the 2-step In-App EFT (Electronic Funds Transfer) Payment workflow we discussed.

## Design Philosophy

The system relies strictly on direct database interactions, bypassing email processors to eliminate friction. 
*   **Students** will upload their POP directly to your secure Firebase Storage bucket.
*   **Admins** will get a centralized dashboard to process them in 1-click. 

